<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-72-0265 </DOCNO><TEXT>We study the region of inhibited radiation in hard hadronic processes.The cases of deep inelastic scattering and Drell-Yan annihilation areconsidered in the semi-inclusive region. A general method to exponentiateleading and next-to-leading logarithms is developed. A complete formulafor the large-N moments is given. The results are shown to agree withprevious two-loop calculations.</TEXT></DOC>